LpexTextViewer
protected class LpexTextViewer.ViewPortGuard
extends com.ibm.swt.events.MouseAdapter
implements com.ibm.swt.events.ControlListener, com.ibm.swt.events.KeyListener, com.ibm.swt.events.MouseMoveListener, com.ibm.swt.events.SelectionListener

Monitors the text portion visible in the text widget. If the portion might have changed, it informs the LpexTextViewer about the potential change and its origin. The origin is used for optimization purposes.
